1323.TW.summary: Yonyu Plastics Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells plastic packaging products worldwide. The company was founded in 1986 and is based in Lukang Town, Taiwan.

1439.TW.summary: Chuwa Wool Industry Co., (Taiwan) Ltd. sells wool tops, superwash wool tops, and seperwash loose wool products in Taiwan. It also leases real estate properties. The company was founded in 1953 and is based in Taipei, Taiwan.

1474.TW.summary: Honmyue Enterprise Co., Ltd. operates as a fabric and textile manufacturer in Taiwan. 1506.TW.summary: Right Way Industrial Co.,Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells automobile parts worldwide. 1598.TW.summary: Dyaco International Inc. designs, manufactures, and distributes fitness, physical therapy, and sports equipment worldwide. It offers automotive seals, including engine, transmission, power steering, axle, shock absorber, and motor seals; and industrial seals comprising pump, gear reducer/gearbox, motor, power tool, robotic arm, wind turbine, and washing machine seals. It provides functional insulation products under the THERMOLITE and CLOMAX brand names; non-woven clothes under the Tyvek name; and paddings, such as vertical folding technology and thermobond fiberfill products.
